Low-cost, and disposable single-material (all-plastic) design. Can be manufactured at scale by die-cutting manufacturing methods.  

Can be shipped in large quantities in a flat or pre-assembled state at state 

Features chin and forehead protection  

Can be cleaned with alcohol-based antiseptic wipes for extended use or re-use  

Can be used with general PPE (surgical mask, N95 respirator, hair net) 

Can be used with stethoscope and other general clinical tools  

Requires assembly by the end user 

Features an adjustable head strap to accommodate all head morphology 

Features a kirigami pattern to provide elasticity to the head strap 
